    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>在HTML和hexo方面完全的小白，此前只懂一点C语言和MATLAB，也没想为了一个博客学完这些东西，遂只有按“想实现什么功能-百度-踩坑-实现功能或者没有”这个流程解决问题。以下是一些记录。</p><hr><h3 id="主页"><a href="#主页" class="headerlink" title="主页"></a>主页</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/Alnasl/picbox/raw/master/img/202112110113327.png"><br>我喜欢那种卡片样式的，简单凝练，信息密度大一点，这个主题为了排版美观失去了信息密集度。所以想改得紧凑。</p><h4 id="橙色部分"><a href="#橙色部分" class="headerlink" title="橙色部分"></a>橙色部分</h4><p>文件路径MyWeb\themes\next\source\css\ _common\components\post\post-header.styl</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.posts-expand .post-header &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  font-size: $font-size-large;</span><br><span class="line">  margin-bottom: 60px;</span><br><span class="line">  text-align: center;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="蓝色虚线框部分"><a href="#蓝色虚线框部分" class="headerlink" title="蓝色虚线框部分"></a>蓝色虚线框部分</h4><p>文件路径MyWeb\themes\next\source\css\ _variables\base.styl</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//  .post-expand .post-eof</span><br><span class="line">//  In Muse scheme, margin above and below the post separator</span><br><span class="line">$post-eof-margin-top          = 10px; //  or 160px for more white space;</span><br><span class="line">$post-eof-margin-bottom       = 10px; //  or 120px for less white space;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="博客标题"><a href="#博客标题" class="headerlink" title="博客标题"></a>博客标题</h3><h4 id="与网页顶部的距离"><a href="#与网页顶部的距离" class="headerlink" title="与网页顶部的距离"></a>与网页顶部的距离</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/Alnasl/picbox/raw/master/img/202112112048693.png"><br>文件路径MyWeb\themes\next\source\css\ _schemes\ _header.styl</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.header-inner &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  padding-top: 40px;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  +mobile() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    padding-top: 50px;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
